attributes.value: The 2025 Open Models Year in Review provides a comprehensive recap of advancements and challenges encountered throughout the year in open models development.

attributes.name: summary
attributes.value: Google DeepMind has enhanced its Gemini audio models, aiming to deliver superior voice experiences and improve user interaction with AI.

attributes.name: summary
attributes.value: A strengthened partnership between Google DeepMind and the UK AI Security Institute (AISI) is being established to focus on critical research in AI safety and security.

attributes.name: summary
attributes.value: The FACTS Benchmark Suite has been introduced to systematically assess the factual accuracy of large language models, indicating a move towards ensuring AI reliability.
